Package: OpennessDataR
Title: Collects and automatically updates data on economic openness
Version: 0.0.9001
Authors@R: person("Claudius", "Graebner", 
  email = "claudius@claudius-graebner.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Collects and automatically updates data on economic openness. It
  accompanies the paper 'Understanding economic openness: A review of existing 
  measures' by Claudius Graebner, Philipp Heimberger, Jakob Kapeller and 
  Florian Springholz.
